    <item>
      <title>Duplicati Nextcloud Backup Script</title>
      <link>https://blog.weiwang.dev/posts/2023/duplicati-nextcloud-backup-script/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Feb 2023 12:15:03 -0500</pubDate>
      <guid>https://blog.weiwang.dev/posts/2023/duplicati-nextcloud-backup-script/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;When Duplicati backups and restores Nextcloud files, we want to enable maintenance mode.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;However by default, Duplicati runs scripts on every operation including when it lists the restore folders, which we don&amp;rsquo;t want.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The following scripts prevents Duplicati from running the script when it&amp;rsquo;s only listing the restore folders.&lt;/p&gt;






&lt;div class=&#34;tabs shadow&#34;&gt;
  
    &lt;input
      type=&#34;radio&#34;
      class=&#34;tab-control hidden&#34;
      name=&#34;tabs-nc_scripts&#34;
      id=&#34;tabs-nc_scripts-0&#34;
      checked=&#34;checked&#34;
    /&gt;
    &lt;label for=&#34;tabs-nc_scripts-0&#34; class=&#34;tab-label&#34;&gt;
      NextcloudOn.sh
    &lt;/label&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hidden tab-content&#34;&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;Script to turn &lt;strong&gt;on&lt;/strong&gt; Nextcloud Maintenance mode&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;#!/bin/bash
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;%DUPLICATI__OPERATIONNAME%&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; !&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;List&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;then&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;  nextcloud.occ maintenance:mode --on
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;fi&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;exit&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  
    &lt;input
      type=&#34;radio&#34;
      class=&#34;tab-control hidden&#34;
      name=&#34;tabs-nc_scripts&#34;
      id=&#34;tabs-nc_scripts-1&#34;
      
    /&gt;
    &lt;label for=&#34;tabs-nc_scripts-1&#34; class=&#34;tab-label&#34;&gt;
      NextcloudOff.sh
    &lt;/label&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;hidden tab-content&#34;&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;Script to turn &lt;strong&gt;off&lt;/strong&gt; Nextcloud Maintenance mode&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Duplicati Setup on Ubuntu</title>
      <link>https://blog.weiwang.dev/posts/2023/duplicati-setup/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Feb 2023 12:07:14 -0500</pubDate>
      <guid>https://blog.weiwang.dev/posts/2023/duplicati-setup/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;package-repository-setup&#34;&gt;Package Repository Setup&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;adding-mono-repository&#34;&gt;Adding Mono Repository&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Add the Mono repository to your system as Duplicati requires mono in order to work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;sudo apt install gnupg ca-certificates
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;sudo apt-key adv --keyserver hkp://keyserver.ubuntu.com:80 --recv-keys 3FA7E0328081BFF6A14DA29AA6A19B38D3D831EF
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;deb https://download.mono-project.com/repo/ubuntu stable-focal main&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/mono-official-stable.list
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;sudo apt update
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;sudo apt install mono-devel gtk-sharp2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;downloading-duplicati&#34;&gt;Downloading Duplicati&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Get the url of the latest version of Duplicat from this &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.duplicati.com/download&#34;&gt;link&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Run wget to download the file. Replace the link below with the link you got from above.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
